<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink370">
<l>vaṇciṉaik kōṅkiṉ ṟaṇkamaḻ paṭalai</l>
<l>yiruñciṟai vaṇṭiṉ peruṅkiḷai moyppa</l>
<l>nīnayan tuṟaiyap paṭṭōḷ</l>
<l>yāva ḷōvem maṟaiyā tīmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Do not hide from us! Who is she that you desired </l>
<l>and with whom you stayed in a cool fragrant shade  </l>
<l>of the Kōṅkam tree with lush branches, </l>
<l>swarmed by the large horde of black-winged bees. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
